        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer38219569" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer421660312671803027">I highly recommend this as a way to peace. It&apos;s different from many other books in that it doesn&apos;t so much tell you what is or what to think, but to get past the illusions of your mind and ego, and get past the tyranny of your imagination to find the reality of love and divinity that&apos;s always been there. It&apos;s a great challenge to the ruts of indoctrinated thought, not only in religion, but in society. It&apos;s a deliberate gateway to an inner revolution.</span>
  <span id="freeText421660312671803027" style="display:none">I highly recommend this as a way to peace. It's different from many other books in that it doesn't so much tell you what is or what to think, but to get past the illusions of your mind and ego, and get past the tyranny of your imagination to find the reality of love and divinity that's always been there. It's a great challenge to the ruts of indoctrinated thought, not only in religion, but in society. It's a deliberate gateway to an inner revolution.</span>
